content: Here's my message to young people: you wouldn't let a bunch of old people decide what music you're going to listen to or what clothes you're going to wear – so don't let them decide your future.Make a plan to vote today: https://t.co/V3uLF7XRqt https://t.co/VR5T97x8K1
